  "texts": [
    "For instance, LLM4Fin [149] pioneered efforts in the FinTech domain by fine-tuning models on a corpus of financial business rules.",
    "Another study [126] conducted a second stage of fine-tuning on a CodeT5 model using developer-written test cases from a single project (e.g., Mockito), significantly improving the model's ability to generate tests that conform to the project's coding conventions and API usage patterns.",
    "Beyond FFT and PEFT, reinforcement learning driven by automated static feedback has also been utilized to optimize test quality attributes [129].",
    "Pre-trainingDistinct from fine-tuning, which adjusts existing knowledge, pre-training aims to endow the model with a foundational understanding of code structure and testing logic from the ground up.",
    "While computationally intensive, it is crucial for building domain-specific foundation models."
